    <stitle>AIR COMPRESSOR: BENDIX TU-FLO 550 AND TU-FLO 750 - REPAIR - INLET VALVES AND SEATS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="repair" graphiccount="0">
        <title>INLET VALVES AND SEATS</title>
        <para>Inlet valves and springs should be replaced. However, if the inlet valve seats show signs of slight nicks
            or scratches, they can be redressed with a fine piece of emery cloth or by lapping with a lapping stone,
            grinding compound and grinding tool. If the seats are damaged to the extent that they cannot be reclaimed,
            they must be replaced.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
